text: Paris Jackson and Cara Delevingne were spotted out on the town in New York! The rumored couple even wore matching outfits for their excursion … so what gives? Are they dating? The pair were spotted hanging out together in New York City just a few hours after they each attended the Longchamp Fifth Avenue store opening on May 3. Paris wore a printed white t - shirt, jeans, and black booties, while the Paper Towns star rocked a strikingly similar ensemble : a white tank top, denim Bermuda shorts and black knee - high boots.
